{"tid":1099680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦呀！我老婆諗嘢真係痴撚線!","createTime":"2019-04-10T02:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T04:03:58.000Z","uid":159290,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f8837201f0d62a0ee55a4876088550772807aed1","tid":1099680,"uid":159290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如題<br />\n話說, 我表弟今個月8歲生日, 咁我老母就諗住問我同我老婆去唔去啦.... 咁都唔喺重點, 個重點係我老母就諗住襯嗰日人多咁就想同埋我老婆一齊搞埋生日(我老婆都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />4月生日)一齊開心吓，咁我就當然覺得好啦！咁正當我老母喺whatsapp問我地 : &quot;去唔去生日會呀？嗰日同埋一齊慶祝啦，不過如果你地唔去嘅話, 咁我就唔一齊搞埋生日架喇。&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實咁樣都好正常呀，你唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪唔幫你預備埋生日囉，咁都喺好循例咁問吓姐，咁如果真係唔嚟嘅，咪唔預備囉&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知我老婆係度發癲就話 : &quot;你老母洗唔洗講到出口呀，幫人慶祝生日都要咁樣講到出口!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot; 跟手就一大堆陰謀論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好辛苦, 好想結束自己嘅生命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 : 啱啱買完KFC早餐舒緩心情"},{"pid":"33d1b41f012ec312a073b0c91490f0dac011de45","tid":1099680,"uid":224168,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"好辛苦呀！樓主打文真係難睇到痴撚線！"},{"pid":"c9f87ee9b60ddce7c016ba2ef6022877954bfbc2","tid":1099680,"uid":28277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:39:28.000Z","msg":"女人諗野不嬲好奇怪"},{"pid":"96d174ff97f572354809cce96aa35bb9923a9d6d","tid":1099680,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"關心吓佢<br />\n壓力大啫"},{"pid":"0b9c49c6410a2aabb623ed9643e84cb827295626","tid":1099680,"uid":67346,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"樓主enter鍵係咪壞咗"},{"pid":"75b65e273551e7972176d7424902371f302ee0f1","tid":1099680,"uid":146535,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"女人忽然痴線<br />\n鍾意嘅人呵返佢就會變返好<br />\n<br />\n女人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都娶左佢，你揀嘅"},{"pid":"6a2966d129d4848fb0776f494094b2fdd813784f","tid":1099680,"uid":171451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"你幫你老婆慶祝生日囉~~~"},{"pid":"8f9ca60cb2b825df4ccef56f4c7fa3d9b5026923","tid":1099680,"uid":236728,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"我阿媽話：傳統只係會幫老人家（長輩）同細路慶祝生日，成人（壯年）唔慶祝。因為驚易死，要「沖喜」喎。<br />\n好似我屋企咁，爸爸同老公生日差幾日，屋企都只係會同爸爸慶祝（老公有出席），唔同我老公慶祝。"},{"pid":"b1f50611dd6596a0f808d461943e44b1c0d8c3cc","tid":1099680,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"我老母都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5f8d4dc73fa6d2743c79ecb27e142b01f519a5","tid":1099680,"uid":162713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:58:16.000Z"